  "name": "Mr. Samsa",
  "description": "The Samsa patriarch who had sunk into lethargy after his business failure, relying entirely on Gregor's income. The transformation forces him back to work as a bank messenger, and with his new uniform comes a renewed sense of authority. He is the most overtly hostile family member, twice driving Gregor back into his room by force \u2014 the second time bombarding him with apples, one of which lodges in his back and never heals.",
